The paper deals with active learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The focus is on the non-realizable case, which involves noise in the data, making it relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and information theory (cs.IT). The use of multi-view setting suggests that the paper may also be relevant to data science (cs.DS).
